    </node>
    <node id="Facebook Ads">
      <data key="d0">Facebook Ads</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Facebook Ads are advertisements on Facebook that can be used for direct and relationship marketing.&lt;SEP&gt;Facebook Ads are advertisements created and displayed on the Facebook platform to reach specific audiences.&lt;SEP&gt;Facebook Ads are advertisements on Facebook that can have social elements and engagement factors.&lt;SEP&gt;Facebook Ads are advertisements created and managed on the Facebook platform to promote businesses and products.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d806f5866af4d4741003d3fe8233a8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-052efb579f52b31e3117bae0de19f737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aca9c55f807e42982283ddc4ea7207b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33bd53c7e23c00189b573a6aef755e00</data>
