      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">FBML stands for FaceBook Markup Language, which is similar to HTML.&lt;SEP&gt;FBML is a markup language used to create custom tabs on Facebook Pages.&lt;SEP&gt;FBML (Facebook Markup Language) is a markup language used to create custom tabs on Facebook Pages, allowing for personalized and interactive content.</data>
